Params: {3: 'The end of the dream is engulfed by an endless white fog.'}
{3: 'Time seems to fade away, and all sound ceases to exist.'}
{3: 'Everything disappears, dissolving into the true domain of the Fog.'}
{3: 'Her decision at parting becomes scissors that, over this unending passage of time, ruthlessly sever all that could be stripped away from herâ€”yet peculiarly sparing her life alone.'}
{3: 'She remains alive, nothing more than alive.'}
{3: 'The buzzing "Key" in her hand serves as her reminder...'}
